Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so in order to be effective then, it's effectively successful, required in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So when I were talking about, well, I want to be successful in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.25,0:00:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,most of the people in this room, I guess about everybody, is guaranteed success with anything you really want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And you say, well, I haven't been successful in this or that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you don't really want to do it then, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.73,0:00:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you sleep last night? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you really wanted to do it, you would have been up working on it, for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.50,0:00:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was working my way through medical school, I didn't go to bed at 8 o'clock at night, for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.25,0:00:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If I got to bed by 3 in the morning, I thought I was really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.59,0:00:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So it takes grit. It takes grit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.04,0:00:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you get the grit? You get the grit from the willingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.07,0:00:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to commit to something gives you the grit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.47,0:00:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're thankful rather than prideful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.78,0:00:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We're okay with progress rather than perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.63,0:01:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We pull into our benefit the willpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.17,0:01:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We pull into our willpower named grit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And we visualize goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.07,0:01:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So visualizations.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.31,0:01:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture yourself in the goal which you want to be a famous movie star.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture yourself then in Hollywood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You chip away incrementally.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.40,0:01:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And you prepare yourself in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.34,0:01:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.71,0:01:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's go to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.09,0:01:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The next characteristics that you need to emphasize in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,These are things that are already within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.39,0:01:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So all we're asking you to do is to increase the,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.25,0:01:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the voltage of things that are already within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.00,0:01:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody has fortitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody dragged themselves out to get here to this lecture and got tickets
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and stood in line and found a seat and put up with a speaker and everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That takes fortitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.12,0:02:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Another trick, and we're talking about the tricks of the world of success,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is to picture the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Have an image in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.03,0:02:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you're destined for someplace, get an image of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.11,0:02:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Get an image of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Get an image of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Get an image of what you want to accomplish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Get an image of your factory spinning out piles and piles of whatever it is you manufacture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture the books lining up that you've written.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the poetry that you've had published.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So picture the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture yourself as successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.81,0:02:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you develop a certain rhythm to your work, a certain work rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.58,0:02:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all the habits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the, you might say, the habits of successful people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortitude, picturing the result, and you develop a certain work rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.05,0:02:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And you develop certain routine schedules.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:03:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And inspiration, then, is the fire underneath your feet that keeps you going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.59,0:03:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Harness the muse, carpe diem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody knows what carpe diem means?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Seize the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Seize the day means today is the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.31,0:03:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Seize the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Seize the day is the day in which you will get an interesting idea, and that will seize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.37,0:03:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So what I was seized by myself, carpe diem, was success is not a consequence of what you do, but what you have become.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that for carpe diem?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.46,0:03:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Success is the result of what you have become, and not necessarily what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All kinds of people try for success, and they seem to be futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They just never make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.09,0:03:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.88,0:03:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:04:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So inspiration, then, harness the muse, carpe diem, seize the day, means to capitalize on opportunities as they arise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people have found that having a special place or setting is very useful to their creating work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're into literary work, like writing books, et cetera, a special place and setting tends to facilitate it, at least with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got all my reference books and everything all around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And the cat's walking back and forth across the desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't write a book without the cat walking over the manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.05,0:04:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Special place and setting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's times when you need expert advice and consultation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you need advice and consultation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And one form of that is the way we use the arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Many times when I'm writing something or I'm preparing a lecture or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll use the arm to confirm it or calibrate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true or not true?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's the level of truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So much of the stuff, if any doubt arises, we use the arm very often.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The more often you use the arm, the better you get at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She knows how to disconnect from any personal involvement in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And the arm is just either stronger or weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't have to tell her what I'm holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a nonverbal phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a phenomena of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with the energy field of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So truth then has a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So here's the secret of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is truth has a reality and exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And that which is not truth has no reality and therefore does not exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So all we're really testing, we're not testing truth against falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're testing is versus is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.32,0:05:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:06:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I hold a certain person in mind, I say they committed that crime, and her arm says
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.81,0:06:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,yes, that's a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's not, if it is not so, it's not a reality, it doesn't exist, and therefore the arm has
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,no strength, and it goes weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So with a little discipline and a little experimentation, every couple has to work out their own technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I hold in mind, I'm not going to be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hold in mind something, then I say to her, I don't tell her what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to influence her at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say what I'm holding in mind is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm holding in mind is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And then she resists.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And does anything come to your mind when I say that, or is it blank?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's blank?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So her mind stays blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And so she's learned how to just let the arm sort of be on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to be able to tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:07:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The falsehood about anything in the universe is an incredible gift in and of itself, is
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.01,0:07:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody ever had that before, except the great ones of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine, you can tell the truth and falsehood about anything in the universe, anytime, anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You can calibrate Cleopatra, Nero, Napoleon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That brings to mind, remember the Elizabeth Smart case?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.61,0:07:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Elizabeth Smart case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The Elizabeth Smart case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The little girl that was missing, you know, in Utah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we were getting a lot of emails at the time to track her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, and we'd say if she's alive, and we'd get yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.31,0:07:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we said, is she in state?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.52,0:07:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And we got no, which was, and we went, whoa, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then a couple days later, we did it again, and this is, I think it was a week or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.97,0:08:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it says, no, she was in Utah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And it really blew our mind, because we couldn't figure it out as to where she was or what was happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, of course, they found her months later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought, well, maybe we're getting weird answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know, they had taken her to Florida and then brought her back into Utah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know, sometimes you get answers, and you can't make sense of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.02,0:08:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, puzzlements, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Puzzlements.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't know why you're getting answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other thing about missing persons, we found we couldn't use it to track missing persons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.49,0:08:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And the reason was that they were somehow involved with karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It was their karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So we couldn't, you know, somebody said, gee, you could locate missing persons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And we asked, could we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And it said, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:09:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And the reason we got a no is because very often it has a karmic background.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.99,0:09:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So, anyway, we just seemed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Seemed like a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Seemed like a good idea at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we could price it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Missing kids, $10.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Under the age of five, $3.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Expert advice and consultation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.65,0:09:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you find somebody you can work with, very often a spouse is the best and not always.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And then with patience and persistence, success becomes closer and closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll move to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang out with successful people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you pick up from their aura a way of being in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Successful people have a recognizable style.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In my life, I've known and met with a lot of the most famous people in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,highly successful people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I was put up for a club one time that was led by all kinds of giants in industry and society,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.67,0:10:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And the one characteristic they all had in common, whether it was the president of J.P.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Morgan or whatever, was cordiality, cordiality, not some secret formula, every one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a guy worth a zillion times more than I am, and his only interest was whether I
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,was comfortable in that chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get you some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You want cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You want sugar?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And look out, the sun is shining and your eyes here are sitting more this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Cordiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Cordiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Multi-billionaire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And his only interest is whether the light's shining in my eye and do I want sugar in my coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's success.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Success is then a way of being, it's a way really of being cordial.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a cordialness towards all of life and all its expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I step over the insect, it's an aspect of my cordiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Cordiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's a stray dog and I try to befriend him, I was in France or someplace, I remember
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.42,0:11:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,sitting in a little cafe, and there's this hungry kitty over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I could not deny this kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.44,0:11:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This kitty, meow, meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So I had to take my lunch and start giving it to the kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.82,0:11:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're cordial towards all of life, whether it's a hungry kitty or it's a bug on the carpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Or it's a person in need or in pain or in suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.12,0:11:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Or somebody needs a ride on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, there's a cordiality towards all of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.73,0:12:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So it means that you have an abundance of the life energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You have more than what you need for just your own survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone here has more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got enough of your own survival and enough energy to radiate out to influence
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,everything around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just think, the fact that you are has decreased the crime rate wherever you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.87,0:12:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you are, not what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No sign that says, burglars beware.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better be carrying an S&W.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:12:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:12:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, they don't know what that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In Arizona.
