Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.39,0:13:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.89,0:13:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't need an S&W warning sign to keep the crooks away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.95,0:13:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What you are just never happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've got a loaded shotgun by the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Never had to shoot anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And get my money's worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping a crook would come by someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.01,0:13:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Second.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.01,0:13:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've practiced with this big shotgun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what you need is a shotgun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody needs a shotgun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And a shotgun has a peculiar sound to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people know the sound of a shotgun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's unmistakable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.83,0:14:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So somebody knocks on my door at 11 o'clock at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I pull it out and it goes, ka-chunk, ka-chunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
