Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound of somebody loading the chamber of a 12-gauge shotgun is unmistakable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You only have to hear it once in your life and you know that sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So we've never had any trouble with robbers or ker-chunk, ker-chunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,One way to be successful is cordiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Cordiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.58,0:14:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,was the prime characteristic of all the world's most famous and rich people that I've ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Every one of them was completely cordial, concerned about my welfare, my happiness, my ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.51,0:15:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They want to introduce you to everybody so that you'll have friends to sit and talk with
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.91,0:15:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,before they leave you with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They make sure you're surrounded by friendliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So caringness for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.12,0:15:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The way to be successful, then, is by cordiality and caringness for the happiness of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're constantly caring for the happiness of others, you don't have to worry about your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's automatic because you create a field, and the field is what uplifts you to a state of happiness yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang out with successful people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.46,0:15:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Avoid naysayers and energy drainers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the negative people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Practice the virtues.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Look for helpful feedback.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Imaginative enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.91,0:15:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Be friendly and upbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Express appreciation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Express appreciation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just saying thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:16:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll notice when you shop in a supermarket or something like that, the girl rings you up and all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say to her, gee, thank you, most of them will go, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say, thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.92,0:16:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They look at you like, thank you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.61,0:16:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thank you for bringing in my purchase.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.11,0:16:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, gee, that's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So you thank everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for their efforts in your behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The clerk in the grocery store who rings you up like that, she's like a mechanical being now, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And you say to her, gee, thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's just a little bright flick of sunshine in her day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She feels better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you said, did you feel better?
