Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Not because of anything, but by virtue of that which you have become.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:17:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You radiate out thankfulness, acknowledgement, and positive energy field to everything and everyone.
