Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything you radiate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as you become more aware, you realize that which you are is recognized by life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.94,0:17:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the life that recognizes you.
